&lt;h3 id="visual-workflow-for-choosing-ai-coding-tools"&gt;Visual Workflow for Choosing AI Coding Tools&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To simplify the process of choosing the right AI coding tool, consider the following decision tree:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code class="language-mermaid" data-lang="mermaid"&gt;graph TD;
